cities.name: Summoneria
cities.description: Summoneria is the creatively named capital city of Summoners.

cities.name: Golden Shore
cities.description: Despite the name, the shore near this city is not made of gold.

cities.name: Swampburg
cities.description: Swampburg is a rundown city near a large swamp and old ruins.

cities.name: Raindrop
cities.description: Raindrop is a mysterious town on a faraway island

cities.name: Tear
cities.description: Tear is a quiet town located on a distant isle.

cities.name: The Eye
cities.description: The Eye is said to be the home to dangerous magical creatures. It is accessible only by flight.

cities.name: Magicburg
cities.description: Despite being surrounded by swamps and ruins, Magicburg is a thriving capital city of the Magicians.

cities.name: The Unnamed City
cities.description: The capital city of the Necromancers. No one ever came back to tell the world what its name is.

cities.name: New Asdfghia
cities.description: New Asdfghia is a city named in ancient language, located at the very end of The Spiral's arm.

cities.name: Grasston
cities.description: Grasston is a small town surrounded by large fields of pretty green grass.

cities.name: Hillside Stop
cities.description: Hillside Stop is a city with beautiful views of the nearby hills.

cities.name: Bratislava
cities.description: Bratislava is the capital city of Slovakia. No one knows how it ended up on The Spiral.

cities.name: Marchway
cities.description: Marchway is a small town surrounded by marches.

cities.name: Bogport
cities.description: Bogport is an old fishing town surrounded by swamps and marches.

cities.name: Fibo
cities.description: Fibo is a strategic city located near the centre of The Spiral.

cities.name: Nacci
cities.description: Naci is an important city near the centre of The Spiral.

cities.name: Running Forest
cities.description: Running Forest is a mysterious city surrounded by ancient woods.

cities.name: Las Las
cities.description: Las Las is a large port city located near an old forest.

cities.name: Chev
cities.description: Chev is a small town on the route from the end of the arm to the centre of The Spiral.
